[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/zulus/extjs-eclipse.png)](https://travis-ci.org/zulus/extjs-eclipse) # Eclipse ExtJS plugin for JSDT This plugin is in alpha stage, at this moment. May be unstable. # Requirements Latest webtools JSDT
Latest kepler release (should work on juno too but I'm not sure for now. # Current features * Class outline * Basic content assist
